          "date": "2015-02-27 11:50:41.000000000",
          "tz": 180
        },
        "subject": "LU-5319 protocol: support for multislot feature",
        "message": "LU-5319 protocol: support for multislot feature\n\nre-use ptlrpc_body's last_xid to transfer 16bit tag. the tag\nwill be used to index an virtual (per-export) slot in last_rcvd\nfile when many concurrent modifying RPCs are in flight.\n\nOBD_CONNECT_MULTISLOT flag.\n\nocd_reqs_in_flight in obd_connect_data specifying the maximum\nconcurrent modifying RPCs.\n\nChange-Id: I1dbbf2aeb2985f79c12eb00b4584fd4a60cf870d\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <alexey.zhuravlev@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
